metadata.name: Leonard Passing
metadata.description:
Comet Leonard was the greatest comet of 2021. 
Also known as C/2021 A1 it is a long period comet discovered by G. J. Leonard at the Mount Lemmon Observatory on January the 3rd 2021. 

I took this picture on December the 5th 2021, it was in the constellation Boötes near NGC5466, a class XII globular cluster.

Size: 3762 × 2620
